{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 7350034}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por resoluci&#xF3;n exenta N&#xBA; 2.105, de 20 de julio de 2007, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, autor&#xED;zase a PESQUERA ITATA S.A. para realizar actividades extractivas en alta mar con la nave &quot;Allip&#xE9;n I&quot;, cuyas caracter&#xED;sticas n&#xE1;uticas son las siguientes:</div><br><div class=\"p\">Se&#xF1;al distintiva&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  CB-4493</div><div class=\"p\">Puerto de Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Valpara&#xED;so</div><div class=\"p\">Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2685</div><div class=\"p\">Eslora de arqueo&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  47,30 m.</div><div class=\"p\">T.R.G. (Internacional)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  786,00</div><div class=\"p\">Manga&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10,40 m.</div><div class=\"p\">Puntal&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  6,00 m.</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  D&#xE9;jase sin efecto la resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 2.128 de 2006, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a.</div><br></div>", "i": 7350035}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Valpara&#xED;so, 20 de julio de 2007.- Mar&#xED;a Angela Barbieri Bellolio, Subsecretaria de Pesca (S). </div></div>", "i": 7350036}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctrina": [], "metadatos": {"tiene_notas": false, "tipos_numeros": [{"tipo": "3", "numero": "2105 EXENTA", "abreviacion": "RES", "descripcion": "Resolucion", "compuesto": "RES-2105 EXENTA"}], "organismos": ["MINISTERIO DE ECONOMÍA", "FOMENTO Y RECONSTRUCCION", "SUBSECRETARÍA DE PESCA"], "titulo_norma": "", "fuente": "", "resumenes": [], "